org.knime.base.data.aggregation.dialogutil

Class ColumnAggregationPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.event.MouseAdapter
      • org.knime.base.data.aggregation.dialogutil.AbstractAggregationPanel<ColumnAggregationTableModel,NamedAggregationOperator,AggregationMethod>
        • org.knime.base.data.aggregation.dialogutil.ColumnAggregationPanel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MouseListener, MouseMotionListener, MouseWheelListener, EventListener

    public class ColumnAggregationPanel
extends AbstractAggregationPanel<ColumnAggregationTableModel,NamedAggregationOperator,AggregationMethod>
    This class creates the aggregation column panel that allows the user to define the aggregation columns and their aggregation method. It is used in the Column Aggregator node which allows to specify a set of aggregation methods for a selected list of columns.
    Since:
    2.6
    Author:
    Tobias Koetter, University of Konstanz
